> Okay, try this:
>
> Goto:
>
> http://www.jcwhitney.com/catsubpic.jhtml?CATID=3004
>
> which is their car cover page. If the above link doesn't work, goto 
> their
> homepage, and SEARCH for car cover, which takes you to above.
>
> Then, goto the bottom of the page, to the WOLF CAR COVERS
> link, and click on:
>
> CLICK HERE FOR PRODUCT AND PRICING DETAILS
>
> Select the year and make (VOLKSWAGEN), then hit NEXT,
>
> Then select the model (MICROBUS)
>
> Then select the fabric type. If you're serious about your cover, select
> one of the top two covers.
>
> Check your order, then hit BUY, and you're on yer way!
